    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo trigesimo sexto, sextodecimo kal. martii,
                        indictione quartadecima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name ref="Rogninus"
                                >Rogninus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Sigismundus">Sismundi</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Iolicta">Iulicta</name></persName> uxor eius quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Guarinus">Guarini</name></persName> quia nos
                        qui supra iugales (…) ubi interfuit notitia <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Fraolmus">Fralmi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> domni imperatoris (…) vendimus et tradimus
                        tibi <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> custodi et
                        rectori <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs> sancti Gilii de <placeName
                                ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals">Tepascio</placeName></orgName>
                        tres videlicet petias de terris nostris que esse videntur in loco et finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/3107" key="#Roads">Piciorano</placeName>. Prima
                        quarum ortus, tenet unum caput in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alterum
                        in terra et media fossa de filio <persName><name ref="Benedictus"
                                >Benedicti</name></persName>, latus in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Pedonectus">Pedonette</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Lanfrancus">Lanfranchi</name></persName>, alterum in terra et
                        media fossa <persName><name ref="Wilicio">Guilicionis</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lanberti</name></persName>. Secunda
                        dicitur <placeName ref="#places/3107">Colognora</placeName>, caput in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Hugo">Ughi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Anglus">Angli</name></persName>, alterum in
                        terra de <persName><name ref="Casalese">Casalesi</name></persName>, latus in
                        terra <persName><name ref="Tuallus">Tualli</name></persName>, alterum in
                        terra (…) filii quondam <persName><name ref="Lambertus"
                            >Lamberti</name></persName>. Tertia caput in terra et media fossa
                        Tualli, alterum in terra et media fossa <persName><name ref="Sigefredus"
                                >Sifredi</name></persName>, latus in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Raginmundus">Ramundini</name></persName>, alterum in via
                        publica. (…) Pro quibus recepimus pro te meritum aureum a <persName><name
                                ref="Wilielmus">Guilielmo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Meritum/launechild">pro solidi quinquecentum quinquaginta</rs>.
                        (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum. (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Luca</placeName>. (…) Fralmus domni imperatoris iudex interfui et
                        subscripsi. Signum manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Thabadinus"
                                >Thabadini</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Robertus"
                                >Ruberti</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Asinus">Asini</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Wido">Guidi</name></persName> germanorum quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Antelminus">Antelmini</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Hugo">Ughi</name></persName>, Sifredi (…),
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bernardus"
                            >Bernardi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Bernardus"
                                >Bernardi</name></persName> rogatorum <rs key="#Witness"
                            >trestium</rs> (sic). (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Winigis">Guinisius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris post traditam
                        complevi et dedi.</ab>
